text.en_US: Hopefully you did the Wave block one first. If not...
Try standing on the middle of the floor pattern first.
This will cause Lea to walk up to the block a bit before grabbing it from this position.
Stand there fire a shot toward the switch.
Right as the block starts moving you grab it without moving.
What's that? How do you face the block without moving?
Oh, you just aim towards the block after firing the shot.
